762
01:10:38.901 --> 01:10:40.277
Lock your doors!

763
01:10:40.361 --> 01:10:41.904
What are they doing?

764
01:10:41.987 --> 01:10:43.697
They're gonna lock up.
Lock themselves in.

765
01:10:43.781 --> 01:10:45.449
These are good people
