781
01:11:22.987 --> 01:11:24.029
Why'd it pick us?

782
01:11:24.113 --> 01:11:25.864
Because you stopped.

783
01:11:26.782 --> 01:11:27.950
We're careful.

784
01:11:29.076 --> 01:11:31.245
We see the warning signs
and. most importantly.

785
01:11:31.328 --> 01:11:32.788
